column5: I would like information on fishing Waskiawaka. If you have been there please respond to post or shoot me a PM. Thanks,
Nice lodge and good outposts. Have fished campbell twice feeds into Pellitier which feed into Waskiawaka. Bigger lake, great fishinghttp://www.travelmanitoba.com/master...=lake&d=search
Thanks for the link. Lots of nice pike on the list. Has anyone fished Waskaiwaka?
